sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant Gateway
    participant Policy as Validation / policy
    participant vLLM
    participant Images as Image worker

    Client->>Gateway: HTTPS request + bearer token
    Gateway->>Policy: Authenticate, rate limit, validate, assign request ID
    alt text generation
      Policy->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions
      vLLM-->>Policy: OpenAI-compatible response
    else image generation
      Policy->>Images: POST /generate
      Images-->>Policy: URL or base64 image result
      Policy-->>Policy: Normalize to gateway response
    end
    Policy-->>Gateway: Sanitized result
    Gateway-->>Client: Response + x-request-id
